          <h2>Overview (Required)</h2>
<p>To be honest, I wanted to use <code>RecyclerView custom LayoutManager</code>.<br>
But it's difficult to catch up in a short time.<br>
So I implemented like this.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1269214/22340325/71f18e2a-e430-11e6-8118-8dc4116fd0ac.png"><img src="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1269214/22340325/71f18e2a-e430-11e6-8118-8dc4116fd0ac.png" width="400" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>
<p>If we use LayoutManager, the users can swipe vertically, horizontally, and diagonally.</p>
